      • subProfile

        public ConstraintProfile<Q> subProfile(javax.measure.Measurable<javax.measure.quantity.Duration> offset,
                              javax.measure.Measurable<javax.measure.quantity.Duration> duration)
        Description copied from class: Profile
        An extension of the profile should implement this method to be able to split the profile up into parts. This method should select a single part of the whole profile.
        Specified by:
        subProfile in class Profile<Constraint<Q extends javax.measure.quantity.Quantity>>
        Parameters:
        offset - The offset of where the subsection of the profile should start. This should always be >= 0.
        duration - The total duration of the new profile. The offset + duration should never be more than the total duration of this profile.
        Returns:
        A new Profile implementation that represents the selected subprofile.
